{"tid":691723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁錦松：香港需要1000萬以上人口","createTime":"2018-06-06T04:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T17:54:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4c24450981b089cf37d3c5a53f167724daeccf","tid":691723,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"前財政司司長梁錦松接受團結香港基金的臉書專頁「政策&bull;正察」訪問，指出特區政府的《香港2030+》推算香港在2030年會有800萬人口，但他認為香港長遠需要1,000萬人以上，因為要支持整個大灣區以至中國的發展，「冇咁上下體量嘅人口係支持唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n梁錦松又強調，香港不只是支持他人發展，而是也為自己，因為在知識型經濟下，最能推動經濟發展、提供到機會予年輕人的就是匯集人才，另一方面吸收全世界的精英在香港發展，為年青人提供機會。<br />\n<br />\n前特首曾蔭權任內也曾提出，要將香港人口長遠增至1,000萬，提升香港地位，務求與倫敦和紐約齊名，政府除鼓勵生育外，亦需吸納外來人才。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/250371/%E6%A2%81%E9%8C%A6%E6%9D%BE%E5%80%A1%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B31000%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F250371%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%259D%25BE%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B31000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=vhjfVoIsUf8uppYeFv%2B2IaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e6f4d1e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/250371/%E6%A2%81%E9%8C%A6%E6%9D%BE%E5%80%A1%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B31000%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人多好辦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc32314c4430a9418ee678b9299dce78aba3fdf","tid":691723,"uid":38671,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"香港富士康化"},{"pid":"d07c365453679ffb57a1b55f9ebf3d96bfdc46d5","tid":691723,"uid":6568